The syntax of the for loop is  :

for (initialization; condition; update) { 
 // body of-loop 
}





code :


for (int i=1; i<=20; i++) {
   System.out.println(i);
}




While Loop:
The syntax for while loop is :
(condition) { 
 // body of the loop 
}

code :
int i = 0;
while(i<=20) {
   System.out.println(i);
   i++;
}




Do-While Loop :
The syntax for the do-while loop is :
do { 
 // body of loop; 
} 
while (condition);


code :
int i = 0;
do {
   System.out.println(i);
   i++;
} while(i<=20);
